* Web application *                 -*-muse-*-

Hammer is a high-quality application framework that showcases tools and techniques for software
engineering practices. 

Features:
    Web application
    Model/View/Template architecture
    Data stored in text files
    Built with 50 tricks
    6 operations for each view
    Command injection for custom actions
    ACL controls 

Process:
    Build incrementally
    Functional tests before code
    Outline of product phases
